      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. It is currently operational but shows signs of age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable dents and scratches, and the interior has some stains and wear on the upholstery. Mechanical components are functional, though some minor maintenance may be required in the near future.",
