    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dependable, no-frills daily driver. While the mechanical components, including the engine and transmission, have been regularly serviced and remain in good working order, the car shows its age aesthetically. You will notice several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the roof, and a few small dings around the door panels. The interior is clean but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the floor mats. It is a solid, reliable car for getting from point A to point B, though it is certainly not a showpiece.",
      "price": 17500.0,
