    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got a few miles of memories but still runs like a charm and looks great parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
